<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٤٢٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6401">مُوسَى بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6858">وُهَيْبٌ </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبُ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4458">عِكْرِمَةَ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ <span class="c2">«لَيْسَ ص مِنْ عَزَائِمِ السُّجُودِ وَرَأَيْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَسْجُدُ فِيهَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>